The class name: Simulation
Responsibility:
1. Initialize list of cars
2. Spawn new cars based on user input
3. Initialize Grid of slots with number of streets based on user input
Collaboration:
1. Grid Class
2. TrafficController Class
3. Car Class

The class name: Grid
Responsibility:

Collaboration:
1. Slot Class
2. Intersection Class
3. TrafficController Class

The class name: TrafficController
Responsibility:

Collaboration:
1. Car Class
2. Intersection Class

The class name: Car
Responsibility:
1. Send message to Slot that Car is occupying slot
2. Send message to TrafficController indicating the direction Car intends to 
   proceed through the intersection when Car is approaching the intersection
3. Receive message from TrafficController indicating whether and how Car 
   should move into the intersection
4. Send message to Simulation that Car has exited the grid
Collaboration:
1. Slot Class

The class name: Intersection
Responsibility:

Collaboration:
1. TrafficController Class
2. Slot Class

